#~ "This file consists in 26 lessons and should allow me to learn Katakana "
#~ "writing for the basics letters and syllables. So lets start with lesson "
#~ "1. Open <guimenuitem>Configure &kvoctrain;... </guimenuitem> in the "
#~ "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu and go to the <guilabel>Thresholds</"
